# Customer test fixtures — contain real F4095 routing, transaction detail,
# item ledger, etc. from production customer databases. Repo is public on
# GitHub, so fixtures stay local-only. The analyzer's auto-rehydrate fixture
# list in Tools/analysis-workbook.html silently falls through when these
# files aren't present (e.g. on the deployed site), so gitignoring them
# doesn't break anything customer-facing.
